episodes.title: The Dismantling Of David E. Taylor's Cult - JMMI Kingdom of God Global Church
episodes.description:
This was a service held at Peacemakers International on September 7, 2025.

We gave some basic information on the history of David E. Taylor, and the havoc he has caused wherever he has gone. We gave some history as to our involvement in the past with warning the public about him.  

The following 2 links are some of the main ways we had spoken up back in 2017:

https://youtu.be/c5Ae3EVp8rQ?si=aiPVDgpkC93V0mQG

https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1B73jhrSkK/

to learn more about our ministry, visit: peacemakersinternational.org

Pastor Steve Upshur
Peacemakers International
